    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/35b4e8944da36d84ca7dca3f06ff6875.poster.avif?t=1751528114\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/35b4e8944da36d84ca7dca3f06ff6875.webm?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/35b4e8944da36d84ca7dca3f06ff6875.mp4?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择特色鲜明的战斗员加入你的队伍</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >率领你的小队，进入纷扰的战场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中获取包罗万象，无奇不有的模组，强化你的战斗角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强大无比的敌人将会考验你的团队和策略</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/abbcb5781d179a0cce2734e5e7662a74.webp?t=1751528114\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/abbcb5781d179a0cce2734e5e7662a74.poster.webp?t=1751528114\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=276 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位玩家的每一次游戏都会有所不同，无论成败，每一次的游戏都会得到科研材料，后勤工程团队会善加利用他们，为你的战斗添砖加瓦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/6b7d1a04fb281205fd1b2ba936422420.poster.avif?t=1751528114\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/6b7d1a04fb281205fd1b2ba936422420.webm?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/6b7d1a04fb281205fd1b2ba936422420.mp4?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >能力各异的角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以出战角色多种多样，他们都有着各自的独特能力和强化路线，灵活敏捷的镰刀客，支援全场的无人机飞手，一枪生一枪死的战地医师等多种角色供您选择</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/d83a486ca258aa2789b459847ed15aad.avif?t=1751528114\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您对我们的游戏感兴趣或者有任何意见建议，欢迎加入我们的Q群或关注我们的社交媒体：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/5f978499adb97fffb57202e798dd46c5.avif?t=1751528114\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p>",
